import React from "react"; import { Accordion, AccordionItem, AccordionButton, AccordionPanel, AccordionIcon } from "@chakra-ui/react"; const Faqs = () => { return (

Frequently Asked Questions

{/* General Questions */}

General Questions

What is your return policy?

We offer a 30-day return policy. You can return any unused product within 30 days of purchase for a full refund. Please visit our Return Policy page for more details.

How do I track my order?

Once your order has been shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email. You can track your order by clicking the tracking link in the email or visiting our Order Tracking page.

Do you ship internationally?

Yes, we offer international shipping. Please check our Shipping Policy page for more information on international shipping rates and delivery times.

Can I change my order after placing it?

Unfortunately, once an order is placed, we cannot make changes to it. However, you can cancel your order within 30 minutes of purchase by contacting our customer support team.

How can I contact customer service?

You can contact us via email at support@ourstore.com or through our Contact Us page on the website. We also offer live chat support during business hours.

What payment methods do you accept?

We accept various payment methods, including credit/debit cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express), PayPal, and other secure payment options. For more details, please refer to our Payment Policy.

 {/* Shipping & Delivery */}

Shipping & Delivery

How long does shipping take?

Standard shipping typically takes 5-7 business days. Expedited shipping options are available at checkout for faster delivery. Delivery times may vary based on your location.

How much does shipping cost?

Shipping costs depend on your location and the weight of your order. Shipping rates will be calculated at checkout.

Do you offer free shipping?

Yes! We offer free standard shipping on all orders over $50 within the U.S. For international orders, please refer to our international shipping policy.

Can I change my delivery address after my order has been shipped?

Unfortunately, we cannot change the delivery address once your order has been shipped. Please double-check your address before completing the checkout process.

 {/* Product Information */}

Product Information

How can I find specific products?

You can use our search bar at the top of the page or browse through our product categories to find what you're looking for.

Are the product images accurate?

Yes, all product images are taken in-house and are an accurate representation of the product. However, please note that colors may vary slightly due to lighting and screen settings.

Do you restock out-of-stock items?

If an item is out of stock, we restock it as soon as possible. You can sign up for an email notification when the product becomes available again.

Can I request a product that is not listed on your site?

We are always expanding our product offerings. If there's a product you would like us to carry, please feel free to contact us, and we'll take your request into consideration.

 {/* Account & Orders */}

Account & Orders

Do I need an account to make a purchase?

No, you can checkout as a guest. However, creating an account will allow you to track your orders, save items to your wishlist, and receive exclusive offers.

How do I create an account?

To create an account, click on the "Sign Up" button in the top right corner of the website and enter your details. Once registered, you'll have access to your account page to track orders and manage preferences.

I forgot my password. What should I do?

If you forgot your password, click on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page. Enter your email address, and we'll send you instructions to reset your password.

How do I cancel my order?

Orders can be canceled within 30 minutes of placing them by contacting our customer support team. Once the order is processed, it cannot be canceled.

 {/* Discounts & Promotions */}

Discounts & Promotions

Do you offer discounts or promotional codes?

Yes, we offer regular promotions and discounts. Be sure to subscribe to our newsletter and follow us on social media for exclusive offers.

How can I use a discount code?

To use a discount code, enter the code at checkout in the "Promo Code" section before completing your order. The discount will be applied to your total.

Can I combine multiple discounts or promo codes?

Only one promo code can be applied per order. If you have multiple discount codes, please select the one that gives you the best value.
); }; export default Faqs;
